    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#oliverio1916"/>, pp. 182-183, n. <citedRange>2</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>9.109</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>019700</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            <p>Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, pp. <citedRange>384-385</citedRange>, number 113 (text)</bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-64479"><name nymRef="#Καλλίμαχος">Καλλίμαχος</name>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-65212"><name type="patronymic" nymRef="#Ὀλυμπιόδωρος">Ὀλυμπιοδώρω</name></persName></persName>
                    <lb n="3"/><persName type="divine" ref="#Kyrana"><name nymRef="#Κυράνα">Κυράναι</name></persName> <w lemma="ἀνατίθημι">ἀνέθηκε</w>.
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Kallimakhos fils d'Olympiodoros a consacré à Cyrène.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Kallimachos son of Olympiodoros dedicated to Cyrene.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Kallimachos figlio di Olympiodoros ha dedicato a Cirene.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The date, wrongly given as second century BC in SEG, has been copied by others. Oliverio used his own formula «<foreign xml:lang="it">buona epoca</foreign>». Rosamilia now 
                places it more precisely in the first third of the third century BC., a period with many dedications by individuals.</p>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
